data.description: So much better than new!  This meticulously maintained home is move in ready with gorgeous upgrades and OWNED SOLAR. The low maintenance backyard is already installed complete with a raised garden box!  Boasting over 2000 square feet, this floorplan has an expansive layout, oversized garage, large covered patio, 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 bathrooms as well as bonus room. You will find that the quartz counters, a custom kitchen backsplash and upgraded hardware add charm and class to the space. Special touches abound with designer paint, linen wall treatment and the framed mirror in the bathroom.  Living in this vibrant 55+ community offers a real lifestyle experience!  Be sure to explore the Ranch House, gym, pool, wine tasting room, bocce courts, pickle ball courts, community garden and dog park.  You will love the opportunities to live a relaxed lifestyle here in the heart of the California Delta in this truly special home.
